| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0745 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 26ec9e73-f0d1-56e9-b3c3-98d4f5096b90"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
